FAQ_SUBTITLE_PLACEHOLDER_TEXT: Everything you need to know about our laundry pickup and delivery service
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_1: How does your laundry pickup and delivery service work?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_1: Our service is simple: schedule a pickup through our app, we collect your laundry, clean it at our partner facilities, and deliver it back to you at your chosen time. It's convenient, fast, and hassle-free!
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_2: We currently operate in major metropolitan areas. Check our app for specific coverage in your location. We're continuously expanding our service area to reach more customers.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_3: How much does the service cost?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_3: Our pricing is based on weight and specific laundry needs. You can get an instant quote through our app by entering your laundry details. We offer competitive rates and various package options to suit different budgets.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_4: What if I'm not home for pickup or delivery?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_4: No problem! You can specify a safe place for pickup and delivery in the app. Alternatively, you can authorize us to collect from or deliver to a neighbor or your building's reception area.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_5: How do you ensure the quality of cleaning?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_5: We partner with top-rated, professional laundry facilities that adhere to strict quality standards. All items are carefully sorted, cleaned, and inspected before delivery. We also offer a satisfaction guarantee on all our services.
ACCORDION_QUESTION_1: How does your laundry pickup and delivery service work?
ACCORDION_ANSWER_1: Our service is simple and convenient. Schedule a pickup through our app, we'll collect your laundry, clean it at our partner facilities, and deliver it back to you fresh and folded at your chosen time.
ACCORDION_ANSWER_2: We offer standard 48-hour turnaround and express 24-hour service. Same-day service is available in select areas for orders placed before 9 AM.
ACCORDION_QUESTION_3: How much does the service cost?
ACCORDION_ANSWER_3: Our pricing is based on weight or per-item for specialty garments. Standard service starts at $1.50 per pound. Exact quotes are provided in the app after you input your order details.
ACCORDION_QUESTION_4: Is my laundry safe with your service?
ACCORDION_ANSWER_4: Absolutely! We partner with professional, vetted laundry facilities. Your clothes are carefully handled, cleaned, and tracked throughout the process. We also offer insurance for high-value items.
